\",\"$123\",1]]},\"$63\",\"$120\",1]]},\"$63\",\"$112\",1]},\"$63\",\"$110\",1]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"f1:D\"$12e\"\n134:T179d,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch2\u003eJVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe JVC \u003cstrong\u003eGY-HC900C20\u003c/strong\u003e 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder is a professional-grade solution for broadcast, live streaming, and field production. Featuring 3 x 2/3\" CMOS image sensors and a 20x Fujinon ENG zoom lens, the JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder delivers sharp, high-quality visuals with an effective resolution of 2.2 megapixels. It's B4 lens mount with full lens communication that ensures seamless integration with professional lenses, while dual SDXC media recording allows simultaneous capture for redundancy or extended shooting. Designed for live production, the JVC GY-HC900C20 \u003ca href=\"https://www.startech.com.bd/camera/video-camera\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003eVideo Camera\u003c/a\u003e supports 1080p/720p sports exchange standard output and live streaming in 1080p60/50, with internal recording options in H.264 10-bit 4:2:2 at 50 Mb/s and MPEG-2 at 35 Mb/s. Imaging features include a mechanical ND filter wheel (2-, 4-, 6-stop), electronic rolling shutter (1/10000 to 1/6 sec), gain control (-6 to 30 dB), and wide white balance range (2300–15,000K). Operators can choose automatic or manual focus for precise subject control. Connectivity on the JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder is extensive, including dual 3G-SDI outputs, 3G-SDI input, HDMI, composite BNC, Genlock/Timecode, and XLR audio inputs supporting 2- or 4-channel 16-bit 48 kHz audio. Wireless streaming is possible via 2.4 GHz and 5G bands, supporting protocols such as RTMP, RTP, RTSP, UDP, and Zixi. Monitoring is handled via a removable OLED electronic viewfinder (854 x 480) and a fixed 3.5\" non-touch LCD (960 x 540), while GPS tagging allows precise location data. Power is provided through a Gold Mount battery system, with multiple outputs including LEMO and D-Tap. The JVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder is built for professional environments, operating efficiently between 32–104°F (0–40°C) and storing safely at -4–122°F (-20–50°C). Measuring 14.4 x 10.6 x 6.5 inches and weighing 8.6 lb (3.9 kg), this camcorder combines portability, reliability, and high-performance imaging, making the JVC GY-HC900C20 Video Camera a top choice for ENG shoots, live events, and professional broadcasting.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eHDR Recording Options\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder offers advanced HDR recording options for professional-quality imagery. In Extended mode, it achieves a sensitivity rating of f/12 at 60 Hz and f/13 at 50 Hz with 2000 lux, while Standard mode delivers a 62 dB S/N ratio for clear, low-noise footage. HDR capture is available in Hybrid Log Gamma (HLG) or 10-bit J-Log, providing greater dynamic range and flexible post-production grading. Additionally, IP return video and IFB audio streamline communication between the production team and cast/crew, making live shoots and multi-camera setups more efficient and seamless.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eLive Streaming with the JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe JVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder offers advanced live streaming capabilities when used with optional equipment. Its built-in long-range MIMO dual-antenna Wi-Fi unit supports live streaming at up to 1080p60/50 with ultra-low latency of less than 500 ms, ensuring smooth, real-time broadcasts. Additionally, the camcorder includes a LAN terminal and a USB 3.0 host port for flexible wired streaming setups. For enhanced connectivity and reliability, an optional dual-modem bonding unit can be added, allowing simultaneous network connections for stable, high-quality live streams.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eB4 Lens Mount and Broadcast Interfaces\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder is equipped with an industry-standard B4 lens mount, allowing seamless use of professional ENG lenses for versatile shooting. It features an OLED viewfinder for precise monitoring and an IPX2 splash-proof rating, making it reliable in challenging environments. The camcorder offers comprehensive broadcast interfaces, including one HDMI, one composite, two 3G-SDI outputs, and one 3G-SDI pool input, along with a 68-pin fiber connector and XLR audio inputs (one 5-pin and two 3-pin). Additionally, it includes an extra expansion slot for future upgrades, ensuring adaptability for evolving production needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eVersatile Recording\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe JVC GY-HC900C20 Camcorder offers highly flexible recording options to meet professional production needs. It captures 1080p video at up to 120 fps for smooth slow-motion shots and supports 1080p or 720p Sports Exchange Standard format recording for live broadcast compatibility. The camcorder also provides high-quality 50 Mb/s 4:2:2 10-bit H.264 recording, alongside standard MPEG-2 recording at up to 35 Mb/s, giving operators multiple options for both high-fidelity and efficient workflow formats.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eFirmware Upgrade 4.20-0278\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eFirmware Upgrade 4.20-0278 enhances the camcorder’s functionality by adding support for the Canon HJ40ex10B EPF 10-400mm lens with 2x extender, allowing for extended zoom capabilities and greater flexibility in professional shooting. Additionally, it introduces advanced SRT (Secure Reliable Transport) features, including adaptive bit rate, PCR fast mode, and return over IP, ensuring more reliable, high-quality live streaming over IP networks. This upgrade is ideal for broadcasters and live production teams seeking improved lens compatibility and smoother, low-latency streaming performance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eBuy JVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder from Star Tech\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn Bangladesh, you can get the original \u003cstrong\u003eJVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder\u003c/strong\u003e From Star Tech. We have a large collection of the latest \u003ca href=\"https://www.startech.com.bd/jvc-video-camera\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003eJVC Video Camera\u003c/a\u003e to purchase. Order Online or Visit your Nearest \u003ca href=\"https://www.startech.com.bd/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003eStar Tech Shop\u003c/a\u003e to get yours at the lowest price. The JVC GY-HC900C20 2/3\" HD Connected Camcorder comes with 03 Years Service Warranty (No parts warranty).\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"f1:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"content-surface\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Description\"},\"$63\",\"$130\",1],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Full product narrative from the source page\"},\"$63\",\"$131\",1],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"This section is scraped from the live Star Tech product description so the route carries the same long-form context as the source listing.\"},\"$63\",\"$132\",1]]},\"$63\",\"$12f\",1],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"product-description-prose\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$134\"}},\"$63\",\"$133\",1]]},\"$63\",\"$12d\",1]\nf2:D\"$136\"\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"f2:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"content-surface\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Specification\"},\"$63\",\"$138\",1],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Structured specification groups\"},\"$63\",\"$139\",1],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The source table is grouped and normalized so long specs stay readable inside the Atlas layout.\"},\"$63\",\"$13a\",1]]},\"$63\",\"$137\",1],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"cl